@startuml
salt
{
  {#
    . | Skill Forge README alignment check
    Input | README, skills/amadeus-*, .agents/skills/amadeus-*, skill-forge
    Check 1 | Which skills are public entrypoints?
    Check 2 | Which skills are internal workflow steps?
    Check 3 | Do trigger descriptions match the README role?
    Check 4 | Do source skill and promoted artifact differ?
    Check 5 | Is backward compatibility explicitly maintained?
    Outcome | README update / skill contract update / eval or metadata check / no compatibility layer
  }
  {
    [Align README] | [Align skill contract] | [Run skill-forge checks] | [Record follow-up]
  }
}
@enduml
